{"tid":565833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新年夜市　警黑合作　強迫拆除　提醒市民注意衛生banner","createTime":"2018-02-19T11:09:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T15:45:44.000Z","uid":47714,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e20e249d27e697ca23ce53026ee7138ff74fbd40","tid":565833,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T11:09:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10155372514702081&amp;set=a.10150433833777081.350317.690172080&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10155372514702081%26set%3Da.10150433833777081.350317.690172080%26type%3D3%26theater&d=vmKD4W8mTms%2Fq90gnFo94gdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=b3b15129\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10155372514702081&amp;set=a.10150433833777081.350317.690172080&amp;type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：Ng Chungtat<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/yncRrR\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FyncRrR&h=3648edcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說我 Hon Keung Yee Michael Chan 去掛咗幾條「阿媽係女人」既banner<br />\n<br />\n掛起第一條時，已經有半打警察湧埋黎「關切問候」<br />\n<br />\n幾經轉折，先至話識有相熟檔主，成功係佢地後欄掛<br />\n<br />\n正當咁樣擾攘咗近一小時可以功成身退去開餐時，跟住半打黑警，又軍裝又便衣圍住MC哥，話「有勢力、有陀地唔滿意」，強迫佢拆哂落黎<br />\n<br />\n到我同健琳返黎時，佢地又走過黎講返相同既說話<br />\n<br />\n我以為除暴安良、打擊有組織罪案及三合會係警察責任，原來陀地係有權唔畀市民提醒市民注意衛生"},{"pid":"02a420da7a1c150d76ab76e64003a6aad140b3e2","tid":565833,"uid":43189,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T11:26:46.000Z","msg":"一講到警黑合作班五毛就冇晒影<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3710ea1230d47fa03f0163179baced14ea30fa5f","tid":565833,"uid":34103,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T11:30:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1dba08f626f2b0e26a46747244e39cd79af7dea7","tid":565833,"uid":82640,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T11:32:30.000Z","msg":"講